'''方程式组织'''（{{lang-en|Equation Group}}）是一个十分先进而隐秘的计算机间谍活动团体，计算机安全专家Claudio Guarnieri<ref>{{cite news|title=Equation = NSA? Researchers Uncloak Huge 'American Cyber Arsenal'|publisher=''[[Forbes|Forbes]]''|url=http://www.forbes.com/sites/thomasbrewster/2015/02/16/nsa-equation-cyber-tool-treasure-chest/|accessdate=2015-02-17|archive-date=2015-11-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151119101740/http://www.forbes.com/sites/thomasbrewster/2015/02/16/nsa-equation-cyber-tool-treasure-chest//|dead-url=no}}</ref>和一位匿名前情报组织成员<ref>{{cite news |title=Russian researchers expose breakthrough U.S. spying program |publisher=[[Reuters|Reuters]] |url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2015/02/16/us-usa-cyberspying-idUSKBN0LK1QV20150216 |accessdate=2015-02-17 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924213439/http://www.reuters.com/article/2015/02/16/us-usa-cyberspying-idUSKBN0LK1QV20150216 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>怀疑其与[[美国国家安全局|美国国家安全局]]（NSA）有所关联。Equation Group是由[[卡巴斯基实验室|卡巴斯基实验室]]命名，命名的原因是该团体在间谍活动中喜好使用复杂的加密算法和混淆策略。卡巴斯基指出，该团体的恶意软件已感染起码42个国家的500台电脑。<ref>{{cite news|title=How“omnipotent”hackers tied to NSA hid for 14 years—and were found at last|publisher=[[Ars_Technica|Ars Technica]]|url=http://arstechnica.com/security/2015/02/how-omnipotent-hackers-tied-to-the-nsa-hid-for-14-years-and-were-found-at-last/|accessdate=2015-02-17|archive-date=2015-11-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151129223330/http://arstechnica.com/security/2015/02/how-omnipotent-hackers-tied-to-the-nsa-hid-for-14-years-and-were-found-at-last/|dead-url=no}}</ref>据信，该团体与此前发现的[[火焰_(恶意软件)|火焰蠕虫]]及[[震网|震网]]蠕虫的幕后团体存在联系。<ref name="kaspersky">{{Cite news |title=Equation Group: The Crown Creator of Cyber-Espionage |publisher=[[Kaspersky_Lab|Kaspersky Lab]] |url=http://www.kaspersky.com/about/news/virus/2015/Equation-Group-The-Crown-Creator-of-Cyber-Espionage |accessdate=2015-02-17 |archive-date=2015-12-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151202101934/http://www.kaspersky.com/about/news/virus/2015/equation-group-the-crown-creator-of-cyber-espionage |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

== 概要 ==
墨西哥当地时间2015年2月16日举行的「卡巴斯基实验室安全分析师峰会」上，卡巴斯基实验室披露了Equation Group的存在。据介绍，该团体最早的活动可追溯至2001年，更是存在1996年就开始活跃的可能性。团体成员数超过60人。<ref name="kaspersky"></ref>该团体所创造的恶意软件EquationDrug和GrayFish被发现拥有重新编程硬盘固件的能力。<ref>{{Cite web |title=Equation: The Death Star of Malware Galaxy |publisher=[[Kaspersky_Lab|Kaspersky Lab]] |url=https://securelist.com/blog/research/68750/equation-the-death-star-of-malware-galaxy/ |access-date=2015-02-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150217214225/https://securelist.com/blog/research/68750/equation-the-death-star-of-malware-galaxy/ |archive-date=2015-02-17 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>因为该团体的行动高度隐蔽、技术十分先进，所以被认为和美国国家安全局（NSA）的监听项目有关，但卡巴斯基实验室没有明确指出幕后黑手的身份。

